Further Details:
Once a hub of NHP research and development this planet now lies abandoned and under a strict quarentine due to over half the planets surface having been over taken by Id the living City (see Id the Living City for further details).
Folowing what is known as the Id incident the whole planet was evacuated and a quarentine order placed on it, this order included the destruction of the planets moon to preven id using it as a staging ground.
The planet now experiances a delicate equalibrium with Id having agreed to leave the Southen Pole as a neautral landing area.
